headline: CSGP Q2 Deep Dive: Product Expansion and Sales Force Investments Drive Momentum
summary: Real estate data provider CoStar Group (NASDAQ:CSGP) reported revenue ahead of Wall Street’s expectations in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 15.3% year on year to $781.3 million. The company expects next quarter’s revenue to be around $802.5 million, close to analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.17 per share was 23.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
